<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="17Dec1931"><font color="red">17 December 1931</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver): T.S. Eliot has been appointed professor at Harvard and is to leave England next year. Good Lord! Have I to deal with those printers face to face? </div>
